    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "crimsonleafwind@gmail.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "=Quick question about your brand, {{ ($json.name || '').split(' ')[0] }}",
        "emailType": "html",
        "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #0A0A0A; color: #F5F5F0; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); border-radius: 4px;\">\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #C9A84C; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;\">Oivee</h1>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Hey {{ ($json.name || '').split(' ')[0] }},</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">I wanted to personally follow up on your inquiry. Before we jump on a call, I'd love to understand one thing:</p>\n  <div style=\"background: #141414; border-left: 3px solid #C9A84C; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;\">\n    <p style=\"color: #E8D5A3; font-style: italic; margin: 0; font-size: 16px;\">What's the single biggest thing holding your brand back from growing right now?</p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">Is it visibility? Leads? Conversions? A brand that doesn't reflect where you're headed?</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">Hit reply and tell me — even one sentence helps us prepare a more useful strategy call for you.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;\">— Team Oivee</p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6B6B6B;\">\n    Oivee — We make brands impossible to ignore.<br/><a href=\"https://oivee.com\" style=\"color: #C9A84C; text-decoration: none;\">oivee.com</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "email-1",
      "name": "Email 1: Personal Follow-Up",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [1120, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "smtp": {
          "id": "SMTP_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Oivee SMTP"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "amount": 1,
        "unit": "days"
      },
      "id": "wait-2",
      "name": "Wait 1 Day",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1340, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "crimsonleafwind@gmail.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "The #1 mistake brands make with digital marketing",
        "emailType": "html",
        "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #0A0A0A; color: #F5F5F0; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); border-radius: 4px;\">\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #C9A84C; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;\">Oivee</h1>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Hey {{ ($json.name || '').split(' ')[0] }},</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">After working with 50+ brands, we see the same pattern every time:</p>\n  <div style=\"background: #141414; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 4px;\">\n    <p style=\"color: #F5F5F0; font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; margin: 0 0 12px 0;\">They do everything, everywhere, all at once.</p>\n    <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;\">Posting on 5 platforms. Running ads without a funnel. Redesigning the logo every 6 months. The result? Burnt budget, zero compounding, and a brand that looks different on every channel.</p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\"><strong style=\"color: #F5F5F0;\">What works instead:</strong> Pick one channel. Nail the positioning. Build a system that compounds. Then expand.</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">That's exactly what we do at Oivee. We don't scatter your budget — we concentrate it where the math works.</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">Here's a real example: we took a D2C brand from 1.8x ROAS to <strong style=\"color: #C9A84C;\">5.2x ROAS</strong> in one month — by cutting 3 ad channels and doubling down on 1.</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">Tomorrow, I'll share the exact case study.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;\">— Team Oivee</p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6B6B6B;\">\n    Oivee — We make brands impossible to ignore.<br/><a href=\"https://oivee.com\" style=\"color: #C9A84C; text-decoration: none;\">oivee.com</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "email-2",
      "name": "Email 2: Value — Common Mistake",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [1560, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "smtp": {
          "id": "SMTP_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Oivee SMTP"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
