    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "crimsonleafwind@gmail.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "How FreshBrew hit 5.2x ROAS (case study inside)",
        "emailType": "html",
        "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #0A0A0A; color: #F5F5F0; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); border-radius: 4px;\">\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #C9A84C; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;\">Oivee</h1>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Hey {{ ($json.name || '').split(' ')[0] }},</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">As promised — here's the case study.</p>\n  <div style=\"background: #141414; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 4px;\">\n    <p style=\"color: #C9A84C; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;\">Case Study: FreshBrew</p>\n    <p style=\"color: #F5F5F0; font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\">From 1.8x to 5.2x ROAS in 30 Days</p>\n    <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\">FreshBrew was a D2C coffee brand spending across Meta, Google, Pinterest, and influencers. Results were flat. We consolidated to Meta-only, rebuilt their creative strategy around UGC-style reels, and built a proper retargeting funnel.</p>\n    <table style=\"width: 100%; margin-top: 16px;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 12px;\">\n          <p style=\"color: #C9A84C; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0;\">5.2x</p>\n          <p style=\"color: #6B6B6B; font-size: 11px; margin: 4px 0 0;\">ROAS</p>\n        </td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 12px; border-left: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); border-right: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);\">\n          <p style=\"color: #C9A84C; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0;\">+340%</p>\n          <p style=\"color: #6B6B6B; font-size: 11px; margin: 4px 0 0;\">Brand Recall</p>\n        </td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 12px;\">\n          <p style=\"color: #C9A84C; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0;\">12L+</p>\n          <p style=\"color: #6B6B6B; font-size: 11px; margin: 4px 0 0;\">Monthly Revenue</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">This is what happens when you stop doing everything and start doing the right thing.</p>\n  <p style=\"color: #A0A0A0; line-height: 1.7;\">Want to see what a focused strategy could do for <strong style=\"color: #F5F5F0;\">{{ $json.business_name || 'your brand' }}</strong>?</p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;\">\n    <a href=\"https://oivee.com/contact\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: #C9A84C; color: #0A0A0A; padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 14px;\">Book Your Free Strategy Call</a>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color: #6B6B6B; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;\">15 minutes. No fluff. Just an honest look at what would work for you.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;\">— Team Oivee</p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6B6B6B;\">\n    Oivee — We make brands impossible to ignore.<br/><a href=\"https://oivee.com\" style=\"color: #C9A84C; text-decoration: none;\">oivee.com</a><br/><br/>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #6B6B6B; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 11px;\">Unsubscribe</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "email-3",
      "name": "Email 3: Case Study + CTA",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
